Package org.universAAL.utilities.api.service.mid

Contains normal helper classes to deal with Service concepts of universAAL.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UtilActuator
    This is a helper class for those who want to use the typical services of an on/off actuator (get status, set on and off) over an ontological service.
    UtilEditor
    This is a helper class for those who want to use the typical services of an editor (get, add, change and remove) over an ontological service.
    UtilSensor
    This is a helper class for those who want to use the typical services of an on/off sensor (get status) over an ontological service.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidOntologyUtilException  

Package org.universAAL.utilities.api.service.mid Description
